{"tid":1303472,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"保護冰淇淋！防噁客開蓋「亂舔」　警察「冰櫃前」站崗巡邏","createTime":"2019-07-10T10:31:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T10:56:56.000Z","uid":32511,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8f00b3be969a5cb69b7bd10a725138c84b73ff68","tid":1303472,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T10:31:43.000Z","msg":"近日美國德州一間超市出現了奇特景象，只見警察以保護之姿站在冰櫃前，原來是因為先前有人偷偷取出冰淇淋「亂舔」一番，再繼續放回冰櫃中！誇張行徑令警員不得不到超市冰櫃前「站崗」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/07/10/2011759-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F07%2F10%2F2011759-XXL.jpg&h=05a0b06e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n今年六月底，有女子在超市取出一桶冰淇淋，開蓋後「大舔一口」又若無其事的放回貨架上，誇張的行徑被放到網路上後，立刻遭到網友撻伐。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/07/05/2004010-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F07%2F05%2F2004010-XXL.jpg&h=14c23632&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據《華盛頓郵報》報導，由於此影片點閱率出乎意料的高，意外引發部分民眾跟風模仿。其中就有一名黑人男子馬丁（Lenise Martin III），站在超市冰櫃前，將桶裝冰淇淋打開舔了一大口，甚至用手指戳了兩口品嚐，最後再蓋上蓋子，裝沒事將冰淇淋放回冰櫃裡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2019/07/10/2011757-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2019%2F07%2F10%2F2011757-XXL.jpg&h=ec916370&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n事後這兩名「亂舔」冰淇淋的男女皆被警方逮捕，並以惡作劇的罪名被起訴。但各家超市為了防止再有民眾做出這種不衛生的行為，紛紛使出殺手鐧，除了將冰櫃上鎖並貼上「如有需要請找店員幫忙」的告示，德州凱勒市警局甚至派警員到超市的冰櫃巡邏站崗，以「保護冰淇淋」為任務，呼籲民眾切勿再做出違法的行為。"},{"pid":"376fb7c407ceb3c67a6233c45fdbf14255afbbfd","tid":1303472,"uid":250594,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T10:44:08.000Z","msg":"保護隻秋sir<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每塊連儂牆都搵人睇住<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebacb1a1d2e9753ce2ff4d06731d01416dcaa26f","tid":1303472,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T10:44:18.000Z","msg":"cls 力架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da31ba1478afbf5475ba4ba7971e56567fe3f07b","tid":1303472,"uid":101733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T10:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"477955ee84d82090d01cde484539cafcf8afd63e","tid":1303472,"uid":103156,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T10:46:01.000Z","msg":"舒服過守厠所"},{"pid":"fc810ccd897f46f98ccec340b2f1bf7c030fcfa9","tid":1303472,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"477955ee84d82090d01cde484539cafcf8afd63e","tid":1303472,"uid":103156,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T10:46:01.000Z","msg":"舒服過守厠所"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T10:47:39.000Z","msg":"熱咪開個雪櫃抖下涼<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4740f031ed98838658ae9a3add6af87cad2789bd","tid":1303472,"uid":189870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T10:50:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: brown;\">nigga</span>"},{"pid":"9ec46c160ce56e7400be08a4cdf118883d469a0b","tid":1303472,"uid":45523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T10:56:56.000Z","msg":"冰你老母淇淋咩"}]}